snippet.textDisplay: I adore Tati and really like her palette but I agree with you nikki on the critiques you had for it. The sequins are beautiful but unless you pack them and then dont touch them the glitter in them ends up all over my face. The metallics are not "metallic" enough and I end up grabbing metallics from other palletes to make them stronger.  I know Tati recommends using your fingers but I don't like using my fingers to apply my eyeshadow. It's to messy in my opinion. No palette is going to be perfect for everyone and despite me not loving everything about the palette it is one of my favorite palettes. The colors are beautiful and the mattes are super pigmented.
